'''2015年巴基斯坦陸軍Mi-17直昇機空難'''，是指發生於2015年5月8日，一架由{{link-en|巴基斯坦陸軍航空隊|Pakistan Army Aviation Corps}}所駕駛的[[Mi-17直昇機|Mi-17]]運輸直升機墜毀在{{link-en|納爾塔山谷|Naltar Valley}}的事故。當地位於[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[吉尔吉特-巴尔蒂斯坦|吉尔吉特-巴尔蒂斯坦]]的[[吉尔吉特县|吉尔吉特县]]<ref name="tribune"/>，至少有6人死於空難<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1180757/norway-philippines-ambassadors-among-6-killed-in-gilgit-helicopter-crash|title=At least 6 people die helicopter crash in Pakistan|publisher=DAWN|date=2015-05-08|accessdate=2015-05-08|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145035/https://www.dawn.com/news/1180757/norway-philippines-ambassadors-among-6-killed-in-gilgit-helicopter-crash|dead-url=no}}</ref>，死者包括了[[挪威|挪威]]與[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]大使<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/05/08/us-pakistan-crash-idUSKBN0NT0O920150508 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-08 |archive-date=2015-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150508190232/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/05/08/us-pakistan-crash-idUSKBN0NT0O920150508 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="aljazeera.com">{{cite web | url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/05/pakistan-helicopter-carrying-foreign-diplomats-crashes-150508073528072.html | title=Pakistan helicopter carrying foreign diplomats crashes | publisher=AlJAZEERA | date=2015-05-08 | accessdate=2015-05-08 | author=Asad Hashim | archive-date=2018-12-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145043/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/05/pakistan-helicopter-carrying-foreign-diplomats-crashes-150508073528072.html?xif= | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="theguardian">{{cite web | url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/may/08/pakistan-helicopter-crashes-on-school-foreign-diplomats-among-dead | title=Pakistan helicopter crash kills foreign ambassadors | publisher=Guardian | work=theguardian.com | date=2015-05-08 | accessdate=2015-05-08 | author=Jon Boone | archive-date=2018-12-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145051/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/may/08/pakistan-helicopter-crashes-on-school-foreign-diplomats-among-dead+ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC News">{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-32653359 | title=Pakistan helicopter crash kills foreign envoys | publisher=BBC | work=bbc.com | date=2015-05-08 | accessdate=2015-05-08 | archive-date=2018-12-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145044/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-32653359 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
