==事故==
直升機墜入一所[[學校|學校]]建築，目前暫無地面人員傷亡的報導。死者有菲律賓駐巴基斯坦大使[[小多明戈·路森納里歐|小多明戈·路森納里歐]]、挪威駐巴基斯坦大使[[雷夫·H·拉尔森|雷夫·H·拉尔森]]（Leif H. Larsen）、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]與[[印尼|印尼]]大使的[[妻子|妻子]]<ref name="tribune">{{cite web| url =http://tribune.com.pk/story/883013/three-injured-as-helicopter-crashes-in-gilgit/| title =LIVE: Norway, Philippines ambassadors among 6 killed in Gilgit helicopter crash| work =[[The_Express_Tribune|The Express Tribune]]| date =2015-05-08| accessdate =2015-05-08| archive-date =2018-12-26| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145046/https://tribune.com.pk/story/883013/three-injured-as-helicopter-crashes-in-gilgit/| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name="dawn">{{cite web| url =http://www.dawn.com/news/1180757/norway-philippines-envoys-among-6-killed-in-gilgit-helicopter-crash| title =Norway, Philippines ambassadors among 6 killed in Gilgit helicopter crash| work =[[DAWN_(newspaper)|DAWN]]| date =2015-05-08| accessdate =2015-05-08| archive-date =2018-12-26| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145038/https://www.dawn.com/news/1180757/norway-philippines-envoys-among-6-killed-in-gilgit-helicopter-crash| dead-url =no}}</ref> 、兩名駕駛員<ref name="dawn"/>。

[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|巴基斯坦塔利班运动]]聲稱直升機是他們擊落的<ref name="tribune"/>，不過{{link-en|巴基斯坦三軍公共關係處|Inter-Services Public Relations}}（ISPR）則排除了[[恐怖活動|恐怖活動]]的可能性，並稱事故原因是機械故障<ref name="dawn"/>。

此次事故的傷亡人數是由ISPR的處長巴傑瓦（{{link-en|Asim Bajwa|Asim Bajwa}}）[[少將|少將]]在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上公布的<ref name="dawn"/> ，倖存者包括了[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]與[[波蘭|波蘭]]大使，但有不同程度的受伤<ref name="tribune"/>。

